n to sanctioned national identities.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 4aLiterature Studies 2020. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Asian / General.2bisacsh  aFamily Matters.  aFine Balance.  aIndia.  aIndian political history.  aMan Booker Prize.  aParsee.  aRohinton Mistry.  adiaspora.  amigration.  apostcolonial literature.1 aMorey, Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertManchester University Press 1986 - 2013 eBook Packagez978311128363040uhttps://doi.org/10.7765/9781526120656zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781526120656zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781526120656/original  a978-3-11-128363-0 Manchester University Press 1986 - 2013 eBook Packagec1986d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GOA